    Class SlotBlendModes

    Deprecated. The spine-unity 3.7 runtime introduced SkeletonDataModifierAssets BlendModeMaterials which replaced SlotBlendModes. See the SkeletonDataModifierAssets BlendModeMaterials documentation page and this forum thread for further information. This class will be removed in the spine-unity 3.9 runtime.
